Mixing.Description: 100g of graphite powder and 50g of sodium nitrate was stirred into 2.3L of sulfuric acid
60g of potassium permanganate was added while the solution was agitated
Solution removed from ice bath, stirred at 35 Celsius, and then distilled water was added
2.8L of water and 50mL hydrogen peroxide slowly added into the solution

ChooseParameter.Other: The mixture was filtered and washed with 1:10 HCl solution (5L) in order to remove metal ions

Mixing.Description: graphene oxide solution dispersed in 30mL ethanol solution containing octyltriethoxysilane (OTES, 0.5 g) and water (0.5g)
OTES-modified graphene oxide was dispersed in oleic acid solution (30 ml) containing tetrabutyl titanate (3 g) and triethyl amine (2 ml)

ChooseParameter.Other: graphene-TiO2 sheets (with the volume ratio of 2.4:8.5) were washed with dichloromethane 3 times
graphene-TiO2 sheets (with the volume ratios of 2.4:2.0, 2.4:4.8, 2.4:16.8, 2.4:21.6) were washed with tetrabutyl titanate

Drying-Evaporation.Description: Film dried in a vacuum drier

MoldingInfo.Description: Samples were made by hot pressing several solution-cast films stacked together

Electrometry.Description: Frequency range of 10^2–10^7 Hz was analyzed

Dielectric_Loss_Permittivity.description: Frequency dependence of permittivity of the PS composite with 10.9 vol% GT-hybrid sheets

Dielectric_Loss_Tangent.description: Frequency dependence of loss tangent of the PS composite with 10.9 vol% GT-hybrid sheets
